<div>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span style="font-size: medium;">The Learning &amp; Teaching Council is charged with enhancing the quality and scholarship of learning and teaching at BYU-Idaho. This council is comprised of the chairs of seven Learning &amp; Teaching Committees.&nbsp; It is chaired by the Associate Academic Vice President of Instruction. This council meets at least once each semester to coordinate resources from the Academic Office and the efforts of over forty faculty serving on the various committees noted below:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;"><a href="x23093.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">Best Practices Committee</span></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Promote best practices through faculty recognition and gatherings </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Faculty Awards </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Faculty Banquet</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a class="intLink" href="x23939.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Collaboration"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">Collaboration Committee</span></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Foster and share educational practices and ideas for ongoing, extended discussions </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Learning Communities </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Spori Summit Retreats</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a href="x23950.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Dialogue"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">Dialogue Committee</span></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Encourage investigation and sharing of faculty research on learning and teaching </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Brown Bag&nbsp;Lunch Discussions&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Faculty Conference</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a class="intLink" href="x23974.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Publication"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">Publication Committee</span></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Publish findings and insights from faculty including conferences, site visits, and research </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Perspectives Journal </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Learning &amp; Teaching Website stories</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a class="intLink" href="x24000.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Resources"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">Resources Committee</span></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Advertise and allocate resources for Thomas E. Ricks funds </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Thomas E. Ricks Grants</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><a class="intLink" href="x24010.xml" style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;" title="Travel"><span style="color: #4f81bd;">Travel Committee</span></a></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Coordinate selection and travel for faculty groups while developing cross-disciplinary friendships </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Best Practices site visits </span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium;">&middot;Teaching Conferences</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in;"><span style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<span style="font-size: medium; line-height: 1.4em; text-indent: -0.25in;">The council and its related committees are charged with enhancing the quality and scholarship of learning and teaching at BYU-Idaho using tenants of the Learning Model.&nbsp; Faculty members of each college are represented on all committees and work under the direction of the Learning &amp; Teaching Council.</span><br />
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
